news_header: Cargotec reports strong performance in Q3 with increased profits and orders.
news_text: Cargotec, a manufacturer of lifting and load handling equipment, saw a significant improvement in its performance from July to September. The comparable operating profit rose by 14% to EUR 70 million, representing about 12% of net sales. Additionally, orders received increased by 14%, totaling approximately EUR 600 million. CEO Casimir Lindholm noted that this marks the seventh consecutive year of good and stable performance for the company.
